description: The Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid comes packed with all the latest technology and has the usual minivan traits including copious amounts of passenger and cargo space. But its secret weapon is its plug-in hybrid powertrain that provides smooth and punchy acceleration plus an EPA-estimated 32 miles of range without burning a drop of gasoline.
title: 2022 Chrysler Pacifica Plug-in Hybrid

description: Fun to drive, fuel efficient, and surprisingly comfortable (both in terms of seating and ride compliance). I was looking at the GTI and other cars that cost much more money, but randomly decided to test-drive the Integra. What an amazing little car. Plus, the lift back gives it a shocking level of usable space given its size. An automatic Honda Civic Si in a tuxedo -- sign me up!
title: 2023 Acura Integra
